  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Purpose&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    This matrix is used to &quot;trace&quot; relationships between requirements and other project artifacts in order to&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        verify that all requirements are allocated to system components and other project artifacts&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        determine the source of requirements&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        ensure that all requirements are satisfied&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        locate all components and artifacts&amp;nbsp;that are affected as a result of a requirements change, and to assess&#xD;
        impact&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Report Analysis&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;strong>Expected&amp;nbsp;Results&lt;/strong> - All high-level requirements should be fully transformed or covered by&#xD;
    lower-level requirements. The completeness of traceability implies the consistency between each level of&#xD;
    requirements.&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;strong>Missing low-level requirements&lt;/strong> - The team should look at the source and rationale of each untraced&#xD;
    requirement item from Untraced Requirement report and perform root-cause analysis as appropriate. More detail can also&#xD;
    be found at Untraced Requirements.&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    To analyze whether high-level requirements are completely refined into low-level requirements,&amp;nbsp; use the &lt;a&#xD;
    class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../../core.tech.common.extend_supp_metrics-ibm/guidances/supportingmaterials/rqmt_traceability_coverage_AD88731C.html&quot;&#xD;
     guid=&quot;_gZyA8I3-Ed2xw7y9LRwo-A&quot;>Requirement Traceability Coverage&lt;/a> metric.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Collection and reporting tools&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Team Concert&amp;reg;, IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; DOORS&amp;reg;, IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Requirements Composer&amp;reg;, and IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg;&#xD;
    RequisitePro&amp;reg;&amp;nbsp;collect the data needed to produce&amp;nbsp;a Requirements Traceability Matrix.&amp;nbsp; IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg;&#xD;
    Insight&amp;reg; produces a Requirements Traceability Matrix report.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:ContentDescription>
